=9852dd31\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://cameradecision.com/compare/Nikon-D5300-vs-Nikon-D5600</a>"},{"pid":"f7e38f8ff9065cf4b73707ed9a4a88be50dbb233","tid":497570,"uid":51724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T03:56:47.000Z","msg":"機身我覺得有新買新好D，始終又耐用又唔會成日換/再買。"},{"pid":"05d60eb7c8eb1ee7810ad6463d73163b676c9b11","tid":497570,"uid":135381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T12:59:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇岩左呢部 <br />\n想知大家有咩評價 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我自己用緊D5300,性價比係幾高，畫質好過其他同價位既入門機。你唔係成日拍夜景淨係日頭個d 應該都ok，因為佢iso 拉到800/1600以上就好多noise。另外對焦系統唔係好得，好多時我插枝50mm f/1.8 AF 都對唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e57dc0fbb6e202780ed7d41df75e54c6d423c2b","tid":497570,"uid":71341,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T13:31:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8e02e4ef5ad9dbcd3c11dede12f4f375f5ad5105","tid":497570,"uid":99451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T02:28:24.000Z","msg":"用左就快兩年 <br />\n可能我用黎打雀<br />\n想換機了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ecd354f2948da74f108862cc5fed21e6b2359a8","tid":497570,"uid":159969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T19:08:38.000Z","msg":"新手學測光 光圈iso 快門 一流 唔錯嘅拍片機<br />\n加支18-140同50.4 學到好多野同了解到自己有冇耐性學影相 <br />\n除左操點外 好多方面都唔差<br />\n<br />\n利申：當年都用呢部上手用左一年鬆啲 <br />\n宜家做更freelance影product 同 event 拍片"},{"pid":"929279606ec8b6373768d262a2089f5fb158acff","tid":497570,"uid":159969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T19:10:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇岩左呢部 <br />\n想知大家有咩評價 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係想做偽文扮識影相，可以交流下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7890928